# RESTful Applications with Zend Framework 

1. Get source code from github
2. Import database from /db/zendlazada.sql(name database: zenlazada
3. Config site to your server
4. Config files in application/configs
5. Call api
    4.1 Call url:http://zenlzd.localhost/api/count/tags/$tags_id_string
	
